Package: stenR
Title: R6-based Standardization of Raw Discrete Scores 
Version: 0.4.3
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michal",
           family = "Kosinski",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "kosinski.mich@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-8426-3654"))
Description: stenR creates an user-friendly framework to standardize raw discrete
             scores. It provides support for few standard scales often
             used in psychological questionnaires, though also allows using
             custom scales not provided out of the box.
